context.name: Tippmann Arms Hard Sided Rifle Case
context.excerpt: Protect your M4-22 rifle with the Tippmann Arms Hard Sided Rifle Case.
context.content:
Protect your M4-22 rifle with the Tippmann Arms Hard Sided Rifle Case. This case features 4 latches, holes for TSA locks, padded interior and the Tippmann Arms logo moulded into the case.

Measures 42"x10"x4".
